1. *Smatra* se da će biti lep dan. (It is considered that it will be a nice day.)
2. Njegov stav je da svi treba da *smatraju* ovu situaciju ozbiljno. (His view is that everyone should take this situation seriously.)
3. Ona *smatra* da je njeno dete najbolje. (She believes that her child is the best.)
4. Oni *smatraju* da je to najbolje rešenje. (They consider that to be the best solution.)
5. Ona *smatra* da je njena priča tačna. (She believes that her story is true.)